data.description: Enjoy living in this single-story gem located in the Dove Country subdivision. This home boasts a large kitchen with butcherblock countertops and 3 spacious bedrooms complemented by a garage-converted bonus room and an additional media room. The interior has tiled floors that lead you through its open floor plan. Abundant natural light and a roomy patio, perfect for entertaining or a tranquil retreat.
